sequenceDiagram
    participant IDE as IDE
    participant GW as Gateway
    participant SRV as Server
    participant DEV as Device (C++)

    Note over IDE: Operator selects<br/>timestamp T in timeline
    IDE->>GW: rewind_deployment(T)
    GW->>SRV: rewind_deployment command<br/>(async dispatch)
    GW-->>IDE: ACK: sent

    SRV->>SRV: replay_state_at(T)
    Note over SRV: Find nearest snapshot ≤ T<br/>Replay events up to T<br/>→ state S, variables V

    SRV-->>GW: deployment_status broadcast
    GW-->>IDE: state_changed event (preview)

    SRV->>DEV: RestoreState(0x48)<br/>target_state=S, variables=V
    Note over DEV: Pause tick loop<br/>Set currentState ← S<br/>Set variables ← V<br/>Cancel all timers
    DEV-->>SRV: Ack(state_restored)

    SRV->>DEV: Resume
    Note over DEV: Execute from S<br/>with variables V

    SRV-->>GW: command_outcome ACK
    GW-->>IDE: command_outcome broadcast
